//bjorne83 at 2007-07-24 00:14 CET: 
//I have put dvd 2 and 3 in the folder dvd1. and
//everything seems to work, but hven the dvd 2 //installing i got this message: Error location fs //x directory, Help. anybody know???

I got the message "I cannot find [the folder where the folder with files from DVD lies]/FS". The problem was solved by moving the folder with files from DVD to root and renaming it to "FS". 

In brief: AVOID long names and long ways, as well as non-Latin characters in the way to the folder.
